trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Fornece suporte de tempo de design em um designer visual para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl"> </xref> controle.

trans-unit.source: The HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner class is a base class for deriving your own data source designer for a custom data source control derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl> class.
trans-unit.target: A classe HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner é uma classe base para derivar seu próprio designer para um controle de fonte de dados personalizado derivado da <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl>classe</xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceControl> de fonte de dados

trans-unit.source: Other classes that derive from HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner are <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Outras classes que derivam de HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner são <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>e <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDataSourceDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.target: Obtém a coleção de lista de ação para o designer de controle.

trans-unit.target: Obtém um valor que indica se o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.Configure*>método pode ser chamado.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IHierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.Configure*>

trans-unit.source: A design host, such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], uses this property to determine whether to show a **Configure** command in the Smart-Tag menu in design view.

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.DataSourceChanged"></xref> event when the properties of the data source have changed and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*> property value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gera o <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.DataSourceChanged"> </xref> eventos quando as propriedades da fonte de dados tem sido alterado e o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>é o valor da propriedade <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>

trans-unit.source: The OnDataSourceChanged method notifies the designer of each control bound to the associated data source to refresh its control in the design host.
trans-unit.target: O método OnDataSourceChanged notifica o designer de cada controle associado à fonte de dados associado ao atualizar seu controle no host de design.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `false`.
trans-unit.target: Esse método pode ser suprimido com o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>método, ou chamando o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>método com um argumento de `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>

trans-unit.source: Raises the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SchemaRefreshed"></xref> event when the schema of the data source has changed and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*> property value is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gera o <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SchemaRefreshed"> </xref> evento quando o esquema da fonte de dados foi alterado e o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>é o valor da propriedade <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressingDataSourceEvents*>

trans-unit.source: This method notifies the designers of each control bound to the associated data source that the fields in the schema have changed.
trans-unit.target: Este método notifica os designers de cada controle associado à fonte de dados associados os campos no esquema foram alterados.

trans-unit.source: This method can be suppressed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A> method, or by calling the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> method with an argument of `true`.
trans-unit.target: Esse método pode ser suprimido com o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>método, ou chamando o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A>método com um argumento de `true`.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.RefreshSchema%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.HierarchicalDataSourceDesigner.SuppressDataSourceEvents%2A>
